XOTcl SOAP (xotcl-soap) is a protocol plug-in library for the underlying
XOTcl request broker (xorb). It, therefore, provides SOAP support for the 
OpenACS web development toolkit and toolkits (see http://openacs.org) 
derived therefrom, e.g. dotLRN (see http://dotlrn.org). 

